{"tid":1050811,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[圖] 大食MK金毛狗公溝女失敗被捕 吃盡警局還慾求不滿","createTime":"2019-03-07T06:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T13:51:09.000Z","uid":49267,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b23f1e61ca6776a437325df429ef42d28a56f68","tid":1050811,"uid":49267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:37:52.000Z","msg":"江蘇宿遷市一間公安派出所，近日貼出失狗招領廣告，指該隻活潑金毛犬非常大食，希望狗主能盡快認領。<br />\n<br />\n事緣上周三一名狗主帶其飼養的雌性阿拉斯加犬散步時，愛犬被一條雄性金毛尋回犬騷擾，只好報警求助。警員到場後，四處尋找均未能發現尋回犬的狗主，只好帶牠回派出所寄養。<br />\n<br />\n警方「失狗招領」用詞十分生動，不但呼籲狗主速帶十斤狗糧到派出所，最後更特意強調「派出所要被吃到倒閉了！！！！！！」事件引起網民熱議。雖然啟事成功引起市民關注，惟狗主至今尚未現身，金毛尋回犬還需要寄住在派出所一段時間，警員將繼續體會何謂坐吃山崩。<br />\n兩岸組<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jjTcprT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjjTcprT.jpg&h=30c35faf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b066fae381bfa9ca60f430b2e780b3ab64ad66c","tid":1050811,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29763b5e8c69734f4a92ba8ce9d3912cd9f40f70","tid":1050811,"uid":22450,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T06:48:24.000Z","msg":"明明金毛係好靚嘅品種<br />\n唔知點解呢隻咁撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d90f6b5f244aaed3ce07d4d073ca5b5c57b9d31","tid":1050811,"uid":49267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T07:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f605db6b24df2508b8f0bd7c18cb3e2382b3c1d","tid":1050811,"uid":49267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"